headline: Core CPI In Focus With JPMorgan, Goldman, Netflix Set To Report Earnings
summary: This week witnesses earnings from banking giants like JPM, WFC, BAC, BLK. Investors may also look at Core CPI and Core PPI on Tuesday and Wednesday.
